{
  "stem": "56.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father promised him that he'll come and see him the next day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was the first and last time my father went.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He came back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He told my mother, and he told us, that [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Voik ?] propositioned him that since my father knew so many people, and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he would give him everything and take care of us if my father cooperated with him.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my father told him, you-- I'm surprised at you, because you know me, and that you even suggest such a thing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He said, I'd rather starve.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that was the last time my father ever saw [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Voik. ?] But my sister went one morning to see him, and she told him how sick my mother is.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she said, I don't want nothing from you, but tell your wife.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Her being such a good friend of mine, maybe she'll help me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So he told my sister, OK, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I'll tell my wife.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He says, you come back tomorrow morning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my sister used to stand in the doorway.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She used to tell us-- she used to hide.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She didn't want to anyone to see her talking to him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because if you just talk to a German in the criminal police, people would right away point their fingers at you and say you're a cooperator-- collaborator.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So-- because people don't know the relationship we had with this man before the war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, the next morning-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I think my sister told him what was wrong with my mother, because the next morning, he brought a box of vitamin injections.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, you give this to your mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
